public method CommonFunction::C (  ) 

Undocumented Method

# Number of lines of code in C: 7
sub C {
  shift; my ($n,$r) = @_; my $C = 1;
  return(0) if ($r>$n);
  $r = $n-$r if ($r > $n-$r); # find the smaller of the two
  for (1..$r) {$C = ($C*($n-$_+1))/$_}
  return $C;
}
public method CommonFunction::Call (  ) 

Undocumented Method

Code:

# Number of lines of code in Call: 10
sub Call {
  my $self = shift;
  my $fn = shift;
  if ($main::_parser_loaded) {
    return Parser::Function->call($fn,@_)
      if Parser::Context->current->{functions}{$fn};
  }
  return &{$CommonFunction::function{$fn}}(@_) if $CommonFunction::function{$fn};
  return $self->$fn(@_);
}
